  "texts": [
    "The interview participants discussed that the explanations must be concise yet comprehensive and contain the least technical information.",
    "Technical information can be frustrating for lay users since, in most cases, they will not have related technical knowledge or skills.",
    "In addition to that, showing too much information is also associated with users' cognitive load capacity.",
    "If any system displays more than enough information, it becomes cumbersome for users to process it.",
    "The respondents also opined that the explanations need to include information regarding the recommendation's aims and objectives."
  ],
  "correct_citations": []
}